  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1265">
<l>kāṇkamaṟ koṇkaṉaik kaṇṇārak kaṇṭapiṉ </l>
<l>nīṅkumeṉ meṉṟōṭ pacappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>May I look on my lover till I am satisfied and thereafter will vanish the sallowness of my slender shoulders.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
